channel.title: Request a script now with a poll!
channel.description:
Hello, Well as you may know already I have asked for many requests to see what Pay/Free script I should make next. The one with the highest vote I shall make unless I really don't want to make it(un-likely).
So please vote and the poll will close in 3 days.
BTW - We can only see the votes when the poll has finished :D
Thanks! Mad Cow
